\" style=\"width:75%;background:#5c936e\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#5c936e\">High</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"dim-row\">\n  <span class=\"dim-label\">Style / behavior control</span>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:35%;background:#3266ad\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#3266ad\">Surface</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:40%;background:#73726c\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#73726c\">Limited</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:90%;background:#5c936e\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#5c936e\">Deep</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"dim-row\">\n  <span class=\"dim-label\">Scalability</span>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:20%;background:#3266ad\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#3266ad\">Constrained</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:60%;background:#73726c\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#73726c\">Good</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"dim-bar-wrap\">\n    <div class=\"dim-bar\"><div class=\"dim-fill\" style=\"width:80%;background:#5c936e\"></div></div><span class=\"dim-val\" style=\"color:#5c936e\">Strong</span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<hr class=\"div\">\n\n<p class=\"section-label\">When to use which</p>\n<div class=\"verdict\">\n  <p class=\"verdict-title\">Decision guide</p>\n  <div class=\"verdict-items\">\n    <div class=\"verdict-item\">\n      <strong>Prompt engineering</strong>\n      Rapid prototyping, simple tasks, budget-constrained projects, or as a first step before investing in heavier methods.\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"verdict-item\">\n      <strong>RAG</strong>\n      Tasks requiring up-to-date or large-domain knowledge, factual Q&A, document Q&A, and anywhere citations or traceability matter.\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"verdict-item\">\n      <strong>Fine-tuning</strong>\n      Consistent style or tone needed, private/no-domain data that must be baked in, high-volume specialized tasks, or when latency cannot include retrieval.\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
